chris.name: Chris
chris.title: hello
chris.mainbody: Some information about me: My name is Christopher Mooney, I am 17 years old and I am from Philledelphia. Before attending York Tech, I went to school at Central York School District. I decided that I had better career options if I followed over to York Tech and I love working with technology and programming, so it was the logical choice for me. I have always liked using and building pc's, so when I got the opprutunity to do all of that, I took the chance as soon as I can so I was able to follow what I liked doing, and not getting stuck doing something that I hate.

jayson.name: Jayson
jayson.title: hello
jayson.mainbody: My name is Jayson Zeigler and I am go to York County School of Technology for Programming. My home school is Dallastown Area High School. I am 16 years old and I live on the edge of York City. I have a 2003 Nissan Sentra, and I just got my permit.

tyler.name: Tyler
tyler.title: hello
tyler.mainbody: some info about me: Before i went to York Tech i went to Northeastern School ditrict. My favorite color is a blue/green color similar to teal and mint, but my second favorite is dark purple (midnight purple) In my free time i like to work on cars and other fun projects

ethan.name: Ethan
ethan.mainbody: I am a hard working student with a 4.0 GPA. I play basketball and baseball here at York County School of Technology. I am able to adapt to many different work environments. I would prefer to work as a game developer but look to go to college first. I want to be able to build my own game and create a company from it.
